<html>
  <head></head>
  <body style="background-color:silver">
    <p style="font-size:26px">Try to guess the Secret Number!</p>
    <p><strong>~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</strong></p>
    <p>Secret Number range is between <strong><u><em>0 and 100</em></u></strong></p>
    <p><strong>~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</strong></p>
    <p>Your guess was <strong><%= guess %></strong>.
